name: The Child Who Only Wanted To Wake Up On Christmas
description: 1440 x 14600 .PDF - This is a story about death. About childish dreams. About accountability. About responsibility. Every moment of your life has ended and is taken by death. You have been dead longer than you could ever be alive. From the Big Bang until the end of time you were dead vastly longer than you were alive. Editions - Gold Skull Edition - Silver Tongue Edition - Dark Hearts Edition
